                            <value>No</value>
                        </isreviewed>
                        <isautomated>
                            <id>1</id>
                            <value>No</value>
                        </isautomated>
                        <automation_type>
                            <id>0</id>
                            <value>None</value>
                        </automation_type>
                        <preconds>[C1093972]</preconds>
                        <steps>1) Choose bet configuration (line size, coin size, etc).
                            2. Place the bet.
                        </steps>
                        <expected>- Bet should be accepted.
                            - Bet result should be pending outcome (game starts animation/waiting on croupier/etc).
                            - Game should (if shown) display the player&apos;s updated balance (prior to the bet
                            result).
                            - Player&apos;s updated balance should be displayed in Home/profile page (prior to the bet
                            result).
                            - Console should (if shown) display the player&apos;s updated balance (prior to the bet
                            result).
                            - Console controls should be disabled whilst the bet result is being determined.
                            - Console controls should be re-enabled once the bet result is determined (any winnings
                            declared).
                            - Game should (if shown) display the player&apos;s updated balance once the bet result is
                            determined (any winnings declared).
                            - Player&apos;s updated balance should be displayed in Home/profile page once the bet result
                            is determined (any winnings declared).
                            - Console should (if shown) display the player&apos;s updated balance.
                            - Game should be in the ready state to accept further bets.
                        </expected>
                    </custom>
                </case>

