                <case>
                    <id>C47387505</id>
                    <title>Game Device Compatibility</title>
                    <template>Test Case</template>
                    <type>Functionality</type>
                    <priority>Select Priority</priority>
                    <estimate></estimate>
                    <references>OTPI-51</references>
                    <custom>
                        <isreviewed>
                            <id>1</id>
                            <value>No</value>
                        </isreviewed>
                        <isautomated>
                            <id>1</id>
                            <value>No</value>
                        </isautomated>
                        <automation_type>
                            <id>0</id>
                            <value>None</value>
                        </automation_type>
                        <preconds>1) Confirmation of approved list of devices and version from the game provider.
                            2) Get the Intersection from approved devices of Provider and Gamesys approved device
                            list.(NB: The following table updated with the approved list)
                            |||:Device | OS Version| Browser Version |
                            || Samsung Tab | Android 4.4 | Chrome |
                            || Samsung Galaxy S6 edge |Android 7.0 | Chrome |
                            || Samsung Galaxy S5 | Android 7.0 | Chrome |
                            ||iPad Air 2 | iOS v. 10.2.1 | Safari |
                            ||iPhone 5 | iOS v. 10.2.1 | Safari |
                            ||iPhone SE | iOS v. 11.0.3 | Safari |
                            ||iPhone 6 | iOS v. 10.3.3 | Safari |
                            ||iPhone 7+ | iOS v. 10.3.3 | Safari |


                            2) Customer is registered on website.
                            3) Wallet balance of CUR 100.00.
                            4) Find and Launch the game.

                        </preconds>
                        <steps>For each device and browser:
                            1) Rotate device from portrait to landscape.
                            2) Rotate device from landscape to portrait.
                            3) Switch task to any application.
                            4) Switch back to game.
                            5) Press Home key to return to home screen.
                            6) Restore game window (via task manager).
                            7) Press Power button to turn device to standby mode.
                            8) Press Power button to turn device on.
                            9) Interrupt game via call received.
                            10) Disable data/wi-fi mode to simulate connection loss.
                        </steps>
                        <expected>for all the steps

                            1) The game should load and fit in the screen correctly.
                            2) Game UI controls should be displayed correctly.
                            3) Balances should be displayed correctly.
                            4) Home button or Profile button should display correct balance.
                        </expected>
                    </custom>
                </case>

