                        <preconds>1) Customer is registered on website (Starspins supports session limits).
                            2) Wallet balance of CUR 100.00.
                            3) Go to Account section.
                            4) Find and locate Responsible Gaming page.
                            5) Set session limit of 30/60/120 minutes (in test proposal there is 2 second setting).
                            6) Find and launch game.
                        </preconds>
                        <steps>Play game in regular way. Repeat, if necessary, until you reach/nearing session limit.
                        </steps>
                        <expected>Should display Reality Check warning.
                            The Game should be completed.
                            After dismissing Reality Check warning:
                            Game should be in the ready state to accept further bets.
                            Console controls should be re-enabled.
                        </expected>
